snippet.textDisplay: You buy diced onion? LOL! It's literally 30 seconds to dice a whole onion. Chop the sides, cut in half, peel first crappy layer off, then cut/slice about 5 to 7 times without moving the onion apart (keep the onion together while slicing), quarter turn the half you just sliced then cut again 5 to 7 times across, that is one half now diced. Do the other side. Done.
